    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolutely mint, showroom condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and no visible imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine state, smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect, with a full service history and all systems functioning exactly as they did when it first rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks and drives like a brand-new vehicle.",
